languages.text: Некоторые травы, растущие на этом мире, исключены из архивов Магос Биологис и хранятся в тайне. Химикаты, содержащиеся в них, бесценны и могут принести огромную власть владельцу мира.

languages.text: Some of the local herbs are not mentioned in the official records of Magi Biologis and are kept in secret. They contain priceless chemicals that can bring immense power to owner of this world.

traits.locale_text: Some of the local herbs are not mentioned in the official records of Magos Biologis and are kept in secret. They contain priceless chemical compounds that can bring unlimited power to the one who controls them.
